import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

export default function Layout() {
  return (
    <AppBar position="sticky">
        <Toolbar sx={{ width: 640, m:'auto'}}>
            <Typography
            variant = "h4"
            align="center">
                Quiz App
            </Typography>
        </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  )
}
